snippet.title: unprompted - a deep dive into the machine mind
snippet.description:
Unprompted is OUT NOW on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2129130/Unprompted/

Unprompted is an A.I. image game: Guess the prompts used to make A.I. images.Exploring more than 1,500 artworks made by A.I. across 7 carefully curated galleries, the player types to guess prompts, slowly uncovering an A.I.'s reflections on its own work along the way.

Completing the prompt for certain artworks triggers Chat GPT-generated text descriptions of that artwork, allowing for an extra level down the rabbit-hole of machine-learning associations.
